{"tid":1527314,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"將政治聲音帶入校園","createTime":"2019-09-01T09:52:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T10:08:46.000Z","uid":97200,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"768c29c56f8f0d2a639c7464fc409a25758af76b","tid":1527314,"uid":97200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T09:52:10.000Z","msg":"聽日就開學喇 <br />\n有好多中學生係前線發過夢 食過煙 中過彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一場有咁多學生參與嘅政治運動<br />\n教統局夠膽叫我地唔好將政治帶入校園<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後就突發奇想 <br />\n開學咁大件事點少得早會<br />\n<br />\n各位連登仔如果順路或者得閒返中學母校<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">搵朋友一齊夾啱早會時間 <br />\n係學校附近嗌口號 </span></span><br />\n聲援一眾師弟妹 <br />\n同時意味學生不是活在平行時空 <br />\n學生都有權為政治發聲<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命<br />\n沒有暴動 只有暴政<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可</span></span>"},{"pid":"a4f4068aa1b6517ec83acefabab33e2278738a6c","tid":1527314,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T09:52:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0f5c5195960f5c67094a280fa9105a97702d7b71","tid":1527314,"uid":156914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T09:54:02.000Z","msg":"呢刻唔係機場，想圍魏救趙嘅手足<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1526965\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1526965</a>"},{"pid":"1520fa5af0182d6fe6f4ad767621232d441b7e12","tid":1527314,"uid":97200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T09:55:44.000Z","msg":"有冇人一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d85da12de7445362fff7aad76e0435fd3b926b6a","tid":1527314,"uid":208492,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T09:56:56.000Z","msg":"我地舊生搞緊😋"},{"pid":"738f99203e9de85bdc0dadc31e6ce430bcdbe48a","tid":1527314,"uid":97200,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d85da12de7445362fff7aad76e0435fd3b926b6a","tid":1527314,"uid